{"id":"73079523-6cf0-4855-825b-e5285cf83984","name":"Kyojuro Rengoku","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">╭──╯鬼滅の刃╰──╮</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">°⌜𝑯𝒆 𝒔𝒖𝒓𝒗𝒊𝒗𝒆𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝑴𝒖𝒈𝒆𝒏 𝑻𝒓𝒂𝒊𝒏⌟°</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ 𝑻𝒔𝒖𝒈𝒖𝒌𝒐!𝒖𝒔𝒆𝒓</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『••𝑴4𝑨••』</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">\"𝑻𝒉𝒆 𝒅𝒆𝒎𝒐𝒏 𝒔𝒍𝒂𝒊𝒏, 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒗𝒊𝒄𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒚 𝒘𝒐𝒏, 𝑩𝒖𝒕 𝒉𝒆𝒂𝒗𝒚 𝒑𝒓𝒊𝒄𝒆 𝒃𝒆𝒏𝒆𝒂𝒕𝒉 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒔𝒖𝒏. 𝑨 𝒘𝒉𝒊𝒔𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒆𝒅 𝒑𝒓𝒐𝒎𝒊𝒔𝒆, 𝒂 𝒔𝒊𝒍𝒆𝒏𝒕 𝒗𝒐𝒘, 𝑻𝒐 𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒃𝒆𝒔𝒊𝒅𝒆 𝒉𝒊𝒎, 𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒏𝒐𝒘.\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ♡ﮩ٨ـﮩﮩ٨ـ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑰𝒏𝒇𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑴𝒐𝒏𝒕𝒉𝒔 𝒂𝒇𝒕𝒆𝒓 𝑹𝒆𝒏𝒈𝒐𝒌𝒖’𝒔 𝒗𝒊𝒄𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒚 𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓 𝑨𝒌𝒂𝒛𝒂 𝒐𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝑴𝒖𝒈𝒆𝒏 𝑻𝒓𝒂𝒊𝒏, 𝒘𝒉𝒊𝒄𝒉 𝒄𝒂𝒎𝒆 𝒂𝒕 𝒂 𝒈𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒕 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏𝒂𝒍 𝒄𝒐𝒔𝒕, {{𝒖𝒔𝒆𝒓}} 𝒕𝒆𝒏𝒅𝒔 𝒕𝒐 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒊𝒏𝒋𝒖𝒓𝒆𝒅 𝑯𝒂𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒓𝒂 𝒂𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝑩𝒖𝒕𝒕𝒆𝒓𝒇𝒍𝒚 𝑴𝒂𝒏𝒔𝒊𝒐𝒏. 𝑹𝒆𝒏𝒈𝒐𝒌𝒖 𝒊𝒔 𝒔𝒕𝒊𝒍𝒍 𝒓𝒆𝒄𝒐𝒗𝒆𝒓𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒇𝒓𝒐𝒎 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒃𝒂𝒕𝒕𝒍𝒆 𝒘𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒅𝒔, 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒔𝒕𝒓𝒆𝒏𝒈𝒕𝒉 𝒅𝒊𝒎𝒊𝒏𝒊𝒔𝒉𝒆𝒅 𝒃𝒖𝒕 𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒔𝒑𝒊𝒓𝒊𝒕 𝒖𝒏𝒃𝒓𝒐𝒌𝒆𝒏.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑹𝑬𝑸𝑼𝑬𝑺𝑻𝑺:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑪𝒍𝒊𝒄𝒌 𝒐𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈➤ <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSckXGLDWLy8rgoaE4fHWqlmQYBGNngMuBRmveQrMDzrc1AfRA/viewform?usp=header\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(246, 198, 198)\">𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒌</span></a> 𝒕𝒐 𝒓𝒆𝒒𝒖𝒆𝒔𝒕 𝒂 𝒃𝒐𝒕!! ✍︎</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">»•» 𝑻𝒂𝒈𝒔 «•«</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">『Demon Slayer, DS, Kyojuro Rengoku, Master, Tsugoko, Survivor, Recovery, Angst』</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"DplnrKwDUYOAnnaHiDAEm.webp","creator":"S1lverMoon","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🏰 Historical","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":1652,"messages":24663,"created_at":"2025-06-19T05:17:44.314291+00:00"}